title: Likha Diwa Sa Gulod
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Check if uses real fish in any dishes. Sells TVP (textured vegetable protein), vegetarian "fish paste" (bagoong), vegan versions of local dishes, local artwork, and regularly conducts art sessions. Relaxing ambiance.
streetAddress: 1 Lot J. Francisco St. Brgy. Krus na Ligas, UP Diliman, Quezon City
